title: Sam Morril: NYC Class
description: Stand up comedian Sam Morril Joins Kippy and Foley for another round of Are You Garbage? Sam talks about growing up in Manhattan, underage drinking, stand up comedy, and the best snack food.  You know Sam Morril from Tonight Show, Conan, and Comedy Central.  Submit your own AYG questions: AreYouGarbage@gmail.com
